title: Gossip | Watch: Even Jessica Chastain thinks she looks like Bryce Dallas Howard so she pretended to be her
text:
Come on, don't try and say you also haven't gotten them confused at some point too.
Jessica Chastain appeared on with The Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon and Fallon brought up the fact that she's bears a striking similarity to fellow redhead actress Bryce Dallas Howard and Chastain admitted that she constantly gets confused with her The Help costar and, just because, sometimes Jessica just runs with it.
She could fool us anyway.
Via YouTube
